# Scientific plots (data-analysis / shared)

- Prefer helpers in `shared/scientific_plot.py` over one-off rcParams.
- Defaults: Arial 18 pt, inward ticks, consistent legend helpers.
- After changing plot helpers or the example, run `python3 data-analysis/example_scientific_plot.py` and keep `data-analysis/example_scientific_plot.png` in sync when visuals change.
- Save figures under the relevant category folder (usually `data-analysis/`), not absolute machine paths.
